These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  mechanic, pilot, designer
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, boat, helicopter
1. the person driving the van is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
2. the designer is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
3. the person driving the helicopter is between the pilot and the designer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |     3      |
| Job         | pilot | mechanic   | designer |
| Transport   | boat | helicopter | van        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, sprite, almond-milk
3 different pets are kept: snake, goat, mouse
1. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere between the person drinking almond-milk and the owner of the snake##7
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
3. the owner of the goat is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea   | sprite   |
| Pet        | goat | mouse | snake |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-3::.
There 3 different types of food: pumpkin, radish, banana
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, van, bike
1. the person eating pumpkin is not to the left of the person driving the van##8
2. the person eating banana is somewhere between the person eating pumpkin and the person driving the helicopter##7
3. the person eating banana is not to the left of the person driving the bike##8
4. the person eating banana is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |
| Food        | radish | banana | pumpkin |
| Transport   | helicopter       | bike     | van         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  photographer, dancer, pilot
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, thriller, martial-arts
1. the pilot is not to the right of the dancer##8
2. the pilot is on the right of the photographer##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere between the person watching thriller movies and the photographer##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Job           | photographer | pilot | dancer |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts  | time-travel | thriller    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, family, romance
3 different pets are kept: dog, fish, ferret
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
3. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
4. the person watching family movies is not to the right of the person watching disaster movies##8
5. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
6. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | romance | disaster |
| Pet           | fish    | ferret      | dog  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-6::.
