2. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the fisherman##5
3. the police-officer is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
4. the freelancer is on the left of the fisherman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |   2    |       3        |
| Job   | freelancer | fisherman | police-officer |
| Pet   | snake        | bird   | ferret     |

