The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, photographer, security-guard
1. the photographer is between the security-guard and the person drinking coffee##2
2. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the left of the security-guard##8
3. the person drinking coffee is not to the left of the security-guard##8
4. the security-guard is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | fanta | soy-milk | coffee |
| Job        | security-guard      | photographer    | musician |

