.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-8-9::.
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, cauliflower, corn
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, documentary, sports
1. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the left of the person watching sports movies##5
2. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person eating cauliflower##5
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is not to the right of the person eating cucumber##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |
| Food          | corn | cucumber  | cauliflower |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy     | documentary | sports   |

