3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##5
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
5. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage   | fanta | lemonade        | almond-milk    |
| Sport      | baseball  | swimming | skateboarding |

