2. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person drinking soy-milk##7
3. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage   | water     | almond-milk | soy-milk   |
| Hobby      | board-games | video-games | sudoku |

