2. the owner of the ferret is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
3. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the person eating cauliflower##5
4. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |     2     |     3      |
| Food   | kale | cauliflower | mango    |
| Pet    | ferret   | horse      | goldfish |

