3. the person watching crime movies is somewhere between the person watching comedy movies and the person watching fantasy movies##7
4. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the left of the pakistani##8
5. the pakistani is not to the left of the person watching crime movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy   | crime    | fantasy  |
| Nationality   | russian | egyptian | pakistani |

