2. the turkish is not to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
3. the turkish is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |      3      |
| Hobby         | gardening | sudoku | card-games |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | egyptian    | turkish    |

 